snippet.title: Chernobylite 2: Exclusion Zone Early Access Announcement CGI Trailer
snippet.description:
Yes, that's true.
Chernobylite 2: Exclusion Zone is going Steam Early Access on March 6th, 2025!

Add to your wishlist now ➡️ https://store.steampowered.com/app/2075100/Chernobylite_2_Exclusion_Zone/

Also don't forget that the Kickstarter campaign is still ongoing: https://kickstarter.com/projects/thefarm51/chernobylite-2-exclusion-zone-an-open-world-sci-fi-rpg
